    <section id="postingbody">
        <div class="print-information print-qrcode-container">
            <p class="print-qrcode-label">QR Code Link to This Post</p>
            <div class="print-qrcode" data-location="https://pittsburgh.craigslist.org/apa/d/mc-donald-bedroom-15-bath-home-for-rent/7512038170.html"></div>
        </div>
PHONE CALLS ONLY! Please call the number in the contact section and leave a message for Joe if you are interested in seeing this lovely home.<br>
<br>
Newly updated older home in convenient location. Close to Robinson Mall and less than 30 minutes to downtown Pittsburgh. Quiet Washington County neighborhood right next to the Allegheny County border in the Fort Cherry school district . We are offering for rent this recently updated but older three-bedroom home with extra office space and a full basement. The home has laminate floors on the first floor and baths, and carpet in the bedrooms. The kitchen is large enough to eat in, with cherry cabinets and mosaic tile, and includes electric range, microwave, dishwasher and refrigerator. The home features a separate dining room, living room and office area, with a small powder room and laundry area on the first floor. The second floor offers a large master bedroom, and two smaller bedrooms and a full bath. The bath has a double sink vanity, laminate floors and full tub/shower. The master bedroom and second bedroom each have two closets, but this is an older home so unfortunately no walk-ins. The small third bedroom also has a closet.<br>
<br>
There is a full unfinished basement, big front porch and small deck in the back. Large level yard, and detached two-car garage. We have installed a new 90+ fuel efficient gas furnace and A/C. new roof and siding, with extra insulation. Trash pick up is included. You pay for gas, water, sewage and electric and will be responsible for yard maintenance.<br>
<br>
PHONE CALLS ONLY!!!! Please call and LEAVE A MESSAGE. We do not set up appointments via email. To qualify for this home, each occupant or married couple must have good credit and pass the financial analysis done by the credit reporting agency.<br>
<br>
We DO NOT accept Section 8. We DO NOT accept pets.<br>
<br>
YOU MUST MEET THE INCOME AND CREDIT SCORE REQUIREMENTS, NO EXCEPTIONS! There is a $50 PER SINGLE ADULT or married couple credit application fee that is paid to a credit reporting agency that checks your credit and does the financial analysis of your ability to pay. Every adult who lives in the home must sign the lease and pass the credit check. Please, don't waste your time or ours by asking us to ignore your credit history. This fee is non-refundable, pass or fail, per married couple or individual. This means if two single people sign the lease, each person must pay for and pass the credit check. One-year lease, no short-term rentals. We require a one-month security deposit plus the first month's rent to move in.<br>
<br>
We do not accept Section 8. No pets, no exceptions. Phone calls only - leave a message for Joe.
    </section>

